text: Calanthe henryi is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is endemic to Sichuan and Hubei Provinces of China.Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant FamiliesFlora of China v 25 p 307, 疏花虾脊兰 shu hua xia ji lan, Calanthe henryi == References == * China Plant Specialist Group 2004.
